            <title><![CDATA[Blood West DLC ‘Scavengers’ launches June 3]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/blood-west-dlc-scavengers-launches-june-3</link>
            <guid>1511479</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>Wild West <a title="Genres > Stealth [111 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/stealth">stealth</a> <a title="Genres > First-Person Shooter [2,868 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/shooter/fps">first-person shooter</a> <em><a title="Games > Blood West [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/blood-west">Blood West</a></em> downloadable content “Scavengers” will launch on June 3 for $4.99, publisher <a title="Companies > New Blood Interactive [19 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/new-blood-interactive">New Blood Interactive</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Hyperstrange [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/hyperstrange">Hyperstrange</a> announced. <span id="more-1045908"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the content, via its <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4051310/Blood_West_Scavengers/" target="_blank">Steam page</a>:</p><blockquote><p>“Scavengers” brings the long awaited endless <a title="Genres > Roguelite [336 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/roguelite">roguelite</a> mode to <em>Blood West</em>! See how long you can survive as you meet familiar friends and old foes in the never ending weird wild west!</p></blockquote><p><em>Blood West</em> is available for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1587130/Blood_West/" target="_blank">Steam</a>.</p><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>DLC “Scavengers” Release Date Trailer</span></h2><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><iframe title="Blood West: Scavengers - Release Date Announcement" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/T0SpbN7gZKc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/blood-west-dlc-scavengers-launches-june-3]]></content:encoded>
